definitions.body: Egyptain city Je 43:7, Je 43:8, Je 43:9, Je 44:1, Je 46:14, so Je 2:16 Qr (Kt [[תחפנס]]); = [[תְּחַפְנְחֵס]] Ez Eze 30:18; Tafna(i)v [Tafnai]; identif. with Gk. Daphnae, mod. Tel Defenneh, c. 18 m. ESE. from Tanis, c. 9 m. W. of El-Ḳanṭara, Bäd:Egypt. 5th ed. (1902), 169 Petrie:Defenneh (Tanis II), 1888.
